  Similarly, for each `y ‚àà t` we choose `Y y` such that `Set.Ico y (Y y)` is disjoint with `s`.
  Then `‚ãÉ x ‚àà s, Ico x (X x)` and `‚ãÉ y ‚àà t, Ico y (Y y)` are
